latestPosts.caption:
Someone I deeply admire. Someone who gave me an example how to live like yourself on your own terms for all the right reasons. Someone who taught me to do anything in this world but never make Allah talah naraz even if people question you. Someone who stood by me and said “hm hain idhr, abi zinda hain tum kro”

Someone who has always known my secrets and Someone who has always given me a voice for right and wrong. Someone who has always accepted all my transitions. 

My dear lovebirds, 
Thank you for teaching me that life isn’t easy for everyone but you make life easy for your own-self. Thank you for teaching me that you choose your own battles. So choose them wisely. 
Thank you for always smiling and may you always smile and laugh 💕

May you always stay healthy and happy 🤍
Ameen 
Ma sha Allah 💕
Lately have gotten life realisations like never before.
